text: Music from Mars () is a 1955 Czech musical comedy movie directed by Ján Kadár and Elmar Klos and starring Jaroslav Marvan, Josef Bek, Oldřich Nový, Alena Vránová. == Other websites == * Category:1955 musical movies Category:1955 comedy movies Category:Czech musical movies Category:Czech comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Ján Kadár Category:Movies directed by Elmar Klos
